<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038979" n="278r"/>
<opener>Eidem.</opener>
  <p>Quas <date when="1715-12-05">Nonis Decembribus superioris anni</date> ad me dedisti <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517017805501">literas</rs>, suo tem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pore recte accepi. Ex iis non sine dolore intellexi Te <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> longo tempore
                        <lb/>adversa usum valetudine tamque gravibus inco<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odis correptum 
                        <lb/>fuisse, ut <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>lectionibus Academicis omnique co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ercio litera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rio Tibi vacandum fuerit. Gravem tamen quem ex tam tristi nuntio 
                        <lb/>conceperam dolorem haud leviter i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>inutum sensi, postquam leg<unclear>i</unclear> 
                        <pb facs="1038980" n="278v"/>
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <del>d</del><add>t</add>e morb<del>um</del><add>o</add> si non ad pacem saltem ad inducias redacto subjunxeras. 
                        <lb/><del>Spero autem </del>Interim pacem post inducias cum hoste Tuo<!-- Mit "Feind" ist vermutlich die Krankheit gemeint. --> facta Te 
                        <lb/>firma etiamdum valetudine gaudere, spero, certe vehementer <del/><add>exo</add>pto. 
    <lb/><choice><orig>optat</orig><reg>Optat</reg></choice> mecum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentium Lator Patrui mei <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Johannis</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">filius</rs>, Ju<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>venis ornatissimus <add>et profundiores Matheseos c<unclear>a</unclear>llentissimus</add> quem non solum ob paterna sed et ob
                        <lb/>propria merita Tibi optime co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatum fore, Tua in ber<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>noullianam familiam propensa voluntas dubitare non sinit. Con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stituit ille vestris in oris pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> aliquandiu co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>orari, 
                        <lb/><del>virisque doctis</del>cumque in hac sua apud Vos co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oratione Viris 
                        <lb/>doctis, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><del>cipue</del><add>sertim</add> Mathematicis Celebrioribus i<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>otescere cupiat, 
                        <lb/><del>eorumque </del>Tuamque <del>in</del><add>proin pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add>primis exoptet amicitiam, facies ipsi 
                        <lb/>rem gratissimam si eum <add>c</add>onsiliis Tuis juvare et in interiorem 
                        <lb/>amicitiam co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unium studiorum gratia recipere non dedignaberis.
                        <lb/><del>Obstringes sic <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrem</rs> ejus Tibi alias deditum maximo beneficio</del>
<lb/><del>nulloque non officii genere vicissim demerendo. Ipse <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> meus</del>
<lb/><choice><orig>salute</orig><reg>Salute</reg></choice> plurima Tibi dicta hac de re studiose rogatum <add>Te</add> cupit 
    <lb/>certumque esse, se jam alias Tibi deditum beneficio maximo<note type="editorial">Worumstellung</note> nulloque
                        <lb/>non officii genere demerendo <add>hac ratione</add> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te obstrictum iri. Doleo quod opera 
    <lb/>mea in coemendis <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_88AUNP8T">Eruditorum Ephemeridibus</rs> Tibi utilis esse ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que<add>n</add>t, cum desideres eas qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt <del>Ephe</del><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_88AUNP8T"><add>E</add>ditionis <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiensis</rs></rs>, qua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>les apud nos non prostant. Gratissimum autem mihi erit si aliam 
                        <lb/>occasionem mihi subministrabis tuam demerendi benevolentiam<supplied>.</supplied> 
                        <lb/>Interim etiam rogo ut <add>si</add> quod in <add>in</add>scriptione <del>vel prioris vel hujus epi</del>
<lb/>literarum mearum peccatum fu<del>er</del>it, amice condones et corrigas,
                        <lb/>extraneus enim cum sim et con<del/><add>suetor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add> apud Vos titulorum
                        <lb/>ignarus facile errare potui.</p> <closer>C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum <salute>Vale mihique fave.</salute>
<lb/><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>. <date when="1716-03-10">Sexto Iduum Martii MDCCXVI.</date></dateline></closer>
</div>
